00:21:25.598 --> 00:21:29.158
I think the overarching message I'd like to get across is we need to be innovative,

367
00:21:29.358 --> 00:21:31.878
bold, proactive. We need to be thinking about this stuff now.

368
00:21:31.918 --> 00:21:34.718
We can't just wait for the next crisis to come.

369
00:21:34.758 --> 00:21:36.618
We need to actually have a plan.

370
00:21:38.278 --> 00:21:40.718
If we can invest in areas now that save us money later,

371
00:21:42.258 --> 00:21:44.238
we need to be thinking about things that will stick down the track.

